==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Crispin
<hw>Cris"pin</hw> <pr>(kr?s"p?n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
shoemaker; -- jocularly so called from the patron saint of the
craft.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A member of a union or association of
shoemakers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Crisply</ent>⟦br⟧
